Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.48,0:04:31.28,Default - red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1152,931.666)}Furukawa Yuki
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.48,0:04:31.28,Default - white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1138.667,592.999)}Igawa Hiroyuki
